<h1>Data Deletion Policy</h1>

<p>This page explains how you can request the deletion of your data from WiseUpDude.</p>

<h2>Requesting Data Deletion</h2>
<p>To request the deletion of your account and all associated data, please follow these steps:</p>
<ol>
    <li>Log in to your WiseUpDude account.</li>
    <li>Navigate to the 'Account Management' section.</li>
    <li>Select the option to 'Delete Personal Data'.</li>
    <li>Follow the on-screen instructions to confirm the deletion.</li>
</ol>

<p><strong>Please note:</strong> Deleting your data is a permanent action and cannot be undone. All of your quiz history and personal information will be removed from our systems.</p>

<h2>Contact Us</h2>
<p>If you have any trouble with the data deletion process, please contact us for assistance.</p>
